name: Crowbar Climber
summary:
Climb Race Mode is here!
It's time to settle the score in a 1v1 race to the top. Enter the race-exclusive stage with your friend!

Will you take the turtle path, steady and reliable, or the rabbit path, risky but fast? The moment you choose, the race has already begun!

This game is a challenge for all VR gamers who love physics and brain teasers.
For VR gamers who are strong in both mind and arm... see you at the top!
